Question: The same black woman appears in each image, always wearing black and wearing different hairstyles.

Reference Answer: True

Left image URL: http://cdn.playbuzz.com/cdn/68f32bf7-6526-4326-888e-1dd948f2efb3/05c00f7d-e3d0-495c-ba86-135509f56436.jpg

Right image URL: https://i.ytimg.com/vi/_7nArir2dQg/hqdefault.jpg

Program:

```
ANSWER0=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is there a black woman in the image?')
ANSWER1=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is there a black woman in the image?')
ANSWER2=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the woman wearing black?')
ANSWER3=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the woman wearing black?')
ANSWER4=VQA(image=LEFT,question='Is the woman wearing different hairstyles?')
ANSWER5=VQA(image=RIGHT,question='Is the woman wearing different hairstyles?')
ANSWER6=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER0} and {ANSWER2} and {ANSWER4}')
ANSWER7=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER1} and {ANSWER3} and {ANSWER5}')
ANSWER8=EVAL(expr='{ANSWER6} and {ANSWER7}')
FINAL_ANSWER=RESULT(var=ANSWER8)
```
